texts.orig: This charming ranch-style duplex offers a smart investment or a perfect house-hacking opportunity-live in one side and rent out the other! Each unit features 2 bedrooms and 1 full bath, making it a 4 bed / 2 bath property overall. Both sides are move-in ready and fully functional, with vinyl flooring, spacious living rooms, bedrooms with large closets, and full baths with a tub/shower combo. Enjoy relaxing afternoons on the covered rocking chair front porch overlooking the level lot with off-street parking for both units. The backyard is level and open, a perfect place to play games or relax in the sun. Whether you're an investor looking for strong rental potential or a savvy buyer wanting to build sweat equity, this property delivers. Located close to shopping, dining, and entertainment including Walmart, AMC Theatres, Piedmon
